{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join Tom and Lisa in <strong>Hero World 2</strong>, a thrilling new adventure! Unlike the story-driven first installment, this sequel focuses on helping the duo collect fruits while introducing numerous upgrades and fresh features.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key\u00a0Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Expanded Wardrobe for Lisa:</strong> Lisa now has 6 outfits\u20143 more than in the first game\u2014for even more variety and customization.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Level Checkpoints:</strong> Say goodbye to restarting entire levels! New checkpoints let you pick up right where you left off after a misstep.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Larger Levels:</strong> Explore bigger, more detailed levels packed with new challenges and surprises.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Enhanced Gameplay:</strong> Every mechanic has been polished to provide a smoother, more enjoyable experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fresh Content and Features:</strong> Discover all-new elements that make each level more engaging and dynamic.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><br>Hero World 2</strong> builds on the strengths of the first game, delivering an improved and expanded experience with exciting new challenges. Are you ready to join Tom and Lisa on their fruity adventure?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong><br>Note:</strong> Playing the first Hero World can help you get to know the characters and gameplay better.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Available on Steam</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445550/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737655025","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445550/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737655025","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/